ActSupreme Court Act
SubjectCommissioners for Administering Oaths ** Supreme Court of Canada **
PrecisOrder advising that commissions do issue under the Great Seal of Canada EMPOWERING THREE PERSONS TO ADMINISTER OATHS and to take and receive affidavits, declarations and solemn affirmations, within or outside Canada, in or concerning any proceeding had or to be had in the SUPREME COURT OF CANADA.
